      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure it runs perfectly. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s ready for a new home. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come say hi and take it for a spin! \u2728",
