    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a high-pressure Double-VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The chassis retains its factory-spec McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, providing the razor-sharp turn-in the platform is known for. Presented in concours-ready condition with a flawless exterior finish and an immaculate, original interior.",
      "price": 48500.0,
