      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly showroom-standard 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously kept in a climate-controlled environment and presents with a flawless exterior, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The cabin is immaculate, featuring Agate Grey leather that retains its factory scent and original texture, free from any creases or wear. With a mere 12,000 miles, the mechanical performance is indistinguishable from new. Every service has been performed on schedule by authorized technicians, with a complete binder of records included. This is a rare chance to acquire a pristine, collector-grade sports car that includes both original keys, the factory car cover, and the window sticker.",
